    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Whirldz</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Whirldz of snowflakes outside </l>
          <l>Spiral architect designz </l>
          <l>Breathing the dust inside </l>
          <l>A universe of shoebox linez </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>One sock, two sox, three billion free-floatin' microbe-totin' entities </l>
          <l>On a big bang fashion spree </l>
          <l>--fabric re-evolutionariez </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>LIQUIDATION SALE IS ON </l>
          <l>LIQUID NATION SAILING ON </l>
          <l>LIQUIDATION SALE IS ON </l>
          <l>Drowning by water through the fire... </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>...up the ovens, bake the bread </l>
          <l>From the stranger's lofty head </l>
          <l>N' feed a baby from the East </l>
          <l>N' likewise feed it to the beast </l>
          <l>Of Mother Nature's pscyclone floodz </l>
          <l>Her meteor showerz'll dry the blood </l>
          <l>Trade Her gold and precious stonez </l>
          <l>When all your credit haz been blown </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>LIQUIDATION SALE IS ON </l>
          <l>LIQUID NATION SAILING ON </l>
          <l>LIQUIDATION SALE IS ON </l>
          <l>What a pretty planet it wazzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzz...</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
